title: Disney Movie - The Richest Cat in the World (1986)
description:
Cute Disney movie which I liked growing up, video quality isn&#039;t bad at all considering it was ripped from a 20 year old VHS tape. Enjoy

Millionaire Oscar Kohlmeyer has just passed away and leaves most of his estate to his cat Leo. What people don&#039;t know is that Leo is educated and can talk and that Oscar&#039;s wealth; he acquired because of Leo. Now the children of the caretakers discover his secret and keep it to themselves. Oscar&#039;s nephew, Victor, who only got a small inheritance is egged by his greedy wife, Paula, to get rid of Leo so that they can make a claim for the rest of the estate. But Leo is just too wily for them.
